                    </div>
                    <span>Recognition is one of the key management practices that is often overlooked. This book gives the reader lots of easy to implement ideas and a variety of solutions. All managers should keep this practical guide visible in their office. We would all be a lot happier if our efforts were recognized in meaningful ways as suggested by Cindy Ventrice. She gives simple answers to a universal problem.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Make Their Day!</div>
